before the traditional holiday supper his daughters husband like 
many kuwaitis married to americans stayed behind to defend his 
country and relatives 
were happy that martha and the two grandchildren are back 
home safely with us but were still praying for mike davis said 
from koran la we just hope he can get out of there before 
theres a war were wondering about a war 
global worries aside freed hostages want to spend the time 
trying to relax and enjoy a respite from tensions that have 
dominated recent months 
you cant help but think about the politics and the troops 
over there said guy seago an oil worker who was used as a 
